# Version 0.0.9

Changed command-line parsing to use the CmdArgs package;
the usage now looks like

  line2pdf [OPTIONS] [FILE]
    A simple program to convert lines of text into a PDF file.

  Common flags:
    -l --latin     Default encoding
    -b --big5    
    -g --gbk     
       --euc-jp  
       --euc-kr  
    -s --shiftjis
    -? --help      Display help message
    -V --version   Print version information

The small_base flag has been dropped from the Cabal file.

# Version 0.0.8

Minor clean up, no functional changes.
